            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Follow-up to this some years later: it's still a setuptools/distutils issue. It does work in alternative build systems like Meson (I expect skbuild is fine too). So anyone wanting to do this should probably \"just\" switch build system.\n\nIt'd be nice if Cython were able to test clang-cl but unfortunately our tests are very tied to setuptools.",
